{"tid":213052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為有錢佬打強姦案 口賤律師︰女人特別擅長講大話","createTime":"2017-04-23T00:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T03:59:37.000Z","uid":58669,"like":64,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73596b4be2e0231e6b727072ef98318d1129216a","tid":213052,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T00:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170422/large/1492817134_c276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170422%2Flarge%2F1492817134_c276.jpg&h=7c71b950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國一名律師，在一宗強姦案為其當事人辯護時，指女人特別擅長講大話，「因為她們在性別中是弱者」。<br />\n<br />\n田納西州一名富有商人詹尼尼(Mark Giannini，圖)被控在受害人到他家見工時把她強姦，被控3項強姦罪。他的律師法里斯(Steve Farese)在結案陳詞時，指受害人當時同意性交，又質疑其誠信，並作出女人擅長說謊的評論。<br />\n詹尼尼最後被判無罪，受害人則當場哭喊。<br />\n曼菲斯區女性委員會執行總監克拉布(Deborah Clubb)形容法里斯對女性的評語「非常卑劣」。法里斯則表示他的工作「並非要關心有無人受冒犯」，又說「聰明人自會理解」。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"854416c90ef7a183b21ed3599ce5e6ef19ef2812","tid":213052,"uid":17163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T00:45:43.000Z","msg":"咁都冇俾人告性格歧視？"},{"pid":"1a92c82795ea0c4e5601aab3db0ed2664a26b69a","tid":213052,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T00:48:49.000Z","msg":"啲女人好撚古惑架"},{"pid":"028866bc4d69b2d7903de76381f351d57b5691b0","tid":213052,"uid":35317,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"官都判左個女人輸，份新聞仲話佢係受害人，有閪真係大撚曬，唔洗有法治"},{"pid":"b8a3da672f6e81c1fc697b2d8f760fb00a015848","tid":213052,"uid":92673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T01:01:36.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"67ff961a7fb2ac2c505e642215218568501ef74c","tid":213052,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲女人好撚古惑架</blockquote><br />\n出埃及記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/